{"tid":314822,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【淘寶無人cafe】技術未成熟　徐小姐：結算兩次也沒成功","createTime":"2017-07-09T14:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T01:50:36.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d77f18521be9d3a6db17fb4ba6b384e26815bd4f","tid":314822,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170709/large/1499602337_1311.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170709%2Flarge%2F1499602337_1311.jpg&h=f0e0fa35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐小姐：結算兩次也沒成功<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170709/large/1499602339_e010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170709%2Flarge%2F1499602339_e010.jpg&h=e5fce3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杭州居住的連小姐稱，之前看過與無人店有關的短片，今天終於可以體驗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170709/large/1499602340_afb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170709%2Flarge%2F1499602340_afb9.jpg&h=57e7a083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上海來的wendy（左）與萬小姐（右）。<br />\n<br />\n淘寶造物節會場人流如鯽，「淘cafe」體驗店外更是排了長長的人龍，不少人更是遠道而來，只為了體驗其高科技；但亦有買家表示，最後經過玻璃通道時無法辨識扣錢。<br />\n<br />\n特地從上海過來的Wendy表示，雖然排了40分鐘才能進去，但覺得無人店很方便，最後經過玻璃通道「付款」時只需要用正常速度走出來，「跟平常（買單）時間差不多。」<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n在杭州居住的連小姐稱，之前看過與無人店有關的短片，今天終於可以體驗，「進去之後，拿完東西出來也不用刷卡、付現金，沒有手續就出來了，覺得挺新奇的。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，買家徐小姐稱，店內技術似乎仍未成熟，有「甩轆」情況出現，「剛剛我結帳的時候，因為網絡不行，結算兩次也沒成功，可能要網絡好的情況下才比較順利。」<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴集團首席市場官董本洪稱，開設「淘cafe」並非為了一味擴張，「not in a restaurant model（非餐廳經營手法）」，而是展現無人店實際運作情況，未來有意應用在其他實體店。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，阿里作為超級數據公司（super data company），會運用現有數據及技術去協助實體店，以完善用戶體驗，譬如「淘cafe」能夠將店鋪營運情況電子化。<br />\n<br />\n雖然用戶已可在店內消費，不過，他稱「淘cafe」只是作為展現技術之用，技術仍在不斷研發及改善，無意像經營餐廳般一味擴張，亦非要取代人代。<br />\n<br />\n至於未來會否考慮將技術應用在其他線下商店，他則坦承不知道，因為阿里只是負責研發及提供數據與技術，至於會否採用、及如何應用這些數據及技術，則要視乎商家意願。<br />\n<br />\n記者：溫婉婷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56934909&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56934909%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170709&d=fKT5z0tl%2FxQhe5irkuChEIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=830367df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56934909%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170709&h=ec0239c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56934909&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170709</a>"},{"pid":"76cbe0ffa93a18084593a7cfe7dd3632563352e9","tid":314822,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:18:57.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"ca305382cac37b72bc83c68b801b243bafb6a5d4","tid":314822,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:20:23.000Z","msg":"炒 amazon ?<br />\n<br />\n連 amazon 都搞唔掂，大陸會得 ?"},{"pid":"f5bc9b693cfd181ad802ca0fb66f6563a2b9bf0a","tid":314822,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>炒 amazon ?<br />\n<br />\n連 amazon 都搞唔掂，大陸會得 ?</blockquote><br />\n會，唔可以用外國模式去睇大陸"},{"pid":"8982abba17488e18d25a5cf3f61de7a8e7f368e4","tid":314822,"uid":58228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"無人超市 無人cafe 遲下慢慢d底下階層 收銀都無得做"},{"pid":"939d5299546aaa813dd01cdee08cdf1da7e258f4","tid":314822,"uid":33756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T15:58:16.000Z","msg":"喺支那搞無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5197a34e07d3ec7266d9a85cdd2179a4b941e4e","tid":314822,"uid":106,"like":2,"dislike":1,"